[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1103","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1418","title":"ICQ ICQ 99a Web 服务器信息泄露漏洞","description":"ICQ 99a 的 Web 服务器组件（build 1701）在启用 \"Active Homepage\" 功能时存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的文件访问请求，根据服务器返回的差异响应（文件存在时返回 \"404 Forbidden\"，文件不存在时返回 \"404 not found\"）来枚举服务器上的文件是否存在。该漏洞影响 ICQ 99a 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞探测服务器敏感文件路径，为进一步攻击收集信息。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1418"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.923","remediation":"升级 ICQ 至 2000 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，在 ICQ 设置中关闭\"Active Homepage\"（活动主页）功能以消除信息泄露风险。鉴于 ICQ 服务已于 2024 年 6 月 26 日正式停止运营，建议彻底停用 ICQ 并迁移至其他即时通讯软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13508","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/246","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1418.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1418","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1418.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1418.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/icq_vulns.nasl","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/icq_installed.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1418.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/246/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0303","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0303.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0711","title":"Oracle 8.x Unix智能代理oratclsh解释器本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Oracle 8.x Intelligent Agent for Unix系统中包含的oratclsh解释器存在安全缺陷，本地用户可利用该解释器以root权限执行任意Tcl命令，导致权限提升、信息泄露或系统破坏。攻击者需要本地系统访问权限，无需认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0711"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-04-29","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"限制oratclsh解释器的访问权限，移除不必要的setuid位，仅授权可信用户使用Oracle Intelligent Agent组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:30:29.790439238+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92609807906778&w=2","http://marc.info/?t=92550157100002&w=2&r=1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0303.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0305","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0305.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0712","title":"Caldera Open Administration System 敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Caldera Open Administration System (COAS) 存在权限配置不当漏洞，导致系统 /etc/shadow 密码文件被设置为全局可读。攻击者可通过本地访问读取该文件，获取系统所有用户的密码哈希值，进而通过离线破解获得明文密码。该漏洞影响 Caldera 相关操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用前提为攻击者已获得本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0712"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.950","remediation":"立即升级到受支持的现代 Linux 发行版（如 SUSE Linux Enterprise 或 OpenSUSE），Caldera OpenLinux 及 COAS 已停止维护多年，不再提供安全更新。如无法升级，可手动执行 `chmod 600 /etc/shadow` 确保 shadow 文件仅 root 可读，并移除 COAS 的 setuid 二进制文件或卸载 COAS 软件包以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0712","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0712.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0712","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0712.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0712.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7h3x-fvwr-j2mc/GHSA-7h3x-fvwr-j2mc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0712.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/137/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000617.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5fa43793-28e7-4c55-8c2b-61efcb2270d5.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0305.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0222","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0222.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0492","title":"GNU Ffingerd 用户名有效性信息泄露漏洞","description":"GNU Ffingerd 1.19 存在用户信息泄露漏洞。该软件作为 finger 协议的服务端实现，在处理用户查询请求时未对返回结果进行统一处理，导致远程攻击者可通过发送 finger 查询请求并根据服务端返回的差异响应来枚举系统有效用户名。攻击者无需任何认证即可利用此漏洞收集目标系统用户信息，为后续暴力破解或社会工程学攻击提供基础。该漏洞影响 GNU Ffingerd 1.19 及更早版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0492"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-23","updated":"1999-04-23","remediation":"建议立即升级 GNU Ffingerd 至 1.20 及以上版本，该版本修复了用户名有效性泄露问题。如无法升级，可禁用 finger 服务（systemctl disable fingerd）或使用 iptables 限制对 79/TCP 端口的访问，仅允许可信来源连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20327"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0222.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0206","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0206.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0488","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨帧脚本执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 及 5.0 存在跨框架脚本安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意 URL 诱使用户访问，在不同于源安全上下文中执行任意脚本代码。该漏洞属于跨框架变种，利用浏览器同源策略缺陷，可导致敏感信息泄露、会话劫持或权限提升。影响 Windows 平台上的 IE 4.0/5.0 用户，攻击者需诱导用户点击恶意链接，无需额外认证。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0488"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.247","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 Internet Explorer 4.0/5.0，微软已不再提供安全更新。建议立即升级到现代浏览器（如 Microsoft Edge、Chrome、Firefox），并在组策略中禁用 Internet Explorer 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0206.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0209","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0490","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 MSHTML.DLL 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 MSHTML.DLL 组件存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造包含恶意 IMG SRC 标签的 HTML 页面，诱导用户使用 IE 浏览器访问该页面，从而探测目标用户本地文件系统中的文件是否存在及路径信息。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上安装的 Internet Explorer 5.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0490"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.493","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 更高版本（如 IE 6.0 SP1 以上），或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。在 IE 中禁用活动脚本并将 Internet 区域安全级别设为「高」可缓解该信息泄露风险。由于 IE 5.0 已停止支持，建议彻底弃用该版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0127","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0127.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0466","title":"NetBSD SVR4 /dev/wabi 设备文件本地任意文件读写漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.3 及之前版本的 SVR4 兼容层中 /dev/wabi 设备文件主设备编号配置错误，i386 平台错误使用主编号 3（实际应为 2），导致设备文件指向错误的磁盘设备。本地攻击者可利用此缺陷读取或写入磁盘关联的任意文件，造成敏感信息泄露及系统权限提升。利用该漏洞需具备本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0466"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-21","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 NetBSD 1.4 及以上版本（NetBSD-current 19990420 之后已修复），或应用官方补丁 19990419-SVR4_MAKEDEV 后重新运行 SVR4_MAKEDEV 脚本重建 /dev/wabi 设备。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 rm -f /emul/svr4/dev/wabi && mknod /emul/svr4/dev/wabi c 2 2 && chmod 666 /emul/svr4/dev/wabi，将设备主编号从 3 修正为 2。如不需要 SVR4 兼容，建议移除 /emul/svr4 模拟层。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0466"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0127.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0166","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0166.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0491","title":"GNU bash 路径嵌入代码执行漏洞","description":"Bash（GNU bash 1.14 及之前版本）的提示符解析功能存在代码注入漏洞。本地攻击者可在目标目录中创建与待执行命令同名的目录，当其他用户（如 root）进入该目录并执行 bash 时，提示符解析机制会错误地将目录名作为命令执行，导致攻击者以目标用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 GNU bash 1.14 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。利用条件为攻击者需拥有本地账号且能创建目录，并诱导目标用户进入恶意目录。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0491"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.617","remediation":"升级 bash 至 2.0 或更高版本，该漏洞在 bash 2.0 中已修复。如无法升级，避免在多用户环境中使用包含命令替换的 PS1 提示符，并限制非信任用户的本地访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/119","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.10.9904202114070.6623-100000%40smooth.Operator.org","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19095"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0166.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0174","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0174.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0604","title":"Selena Sol WebStore 1.0 信息泄露漏洞","description":"WebStore 1.0 购物车 CGI 程序 web_store.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，由于该 CGI 脚本未正确限制文件访问权限，远程攻击者可通过直接构造特制 HTTP 请求访问服务器上的敏感文件，导致私密信息（如配置文件、数据库凭证等）被非授权泄露。该漏洞影响 Selena Sol WebStore 1.0 版本，攻击无需认证，利用难度低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0604"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.217","remediation":"立即停用 WebStore 1.0，迁移至支持数据库后端存储（而非文件存储）的现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）；如无法立即替换，须将 web_store.cgi 生成的订单数据文件移出 Web 文档根目录（如移至 /var/lib/webstore/），设置目录权限为 700、文件权限为 600，并通过 Web 服务器配置拒绝外部直接访问数据文件路径，同时在搜索引擎中请求移除已索引的敏感信息缓存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0604","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0604.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88033/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000611.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0174.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0178","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0178.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0607","title":"QuikStore quikstore.cgi 敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"QuikStore 购物车系统的 quikstore.cgi 脚本将敏感配置文件 quikstore.cfg 存储在 Web 文档根目录下且未设置充分的访问控制措施，导致远程攻击者可直接通过 HTTP 访问该文件，获取管理员明文密码并进而获得系统管理权限。该漏洞影响 QuikStore 购物车应用，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0607"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.570","remediation":"立即将 quikstore.cfg 移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /etc/quikstore/），并通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 <FilesMatch> 或 .htaccess）禁止公开访问 .cfg 文件；设置文件权限为 600，仅允许 Web 服务器运行用户读取；由于 QuikStore 已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至仍受支持的现代购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0607","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0607.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/q/quickstore.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1983/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ba5d6d065e4a7a2829bd0ee4eca4f1c8ca12a28d/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0178.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0178.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0178.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0243","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0243.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0684","title":"HP HP-UX Sendmail 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统上运行的 Sendmail 8.8.6 存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的邮件请求或恶意数据包，导致 Sendmail 进程崩溃或资源耗尽，从而使邮件服务不可用。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上的 Sendmail 8.8.6 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0684"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.533","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 8.8.6 中的拒绝服务问题。若运行 HP-UX 11i 及更早版本，建议迁移至受支持的 HP-UX 版本或替代 MTA（如 Postfix）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制入站 SMTP 连接源 IP，并监控 MTA 日志中的异常连接行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0684","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0684.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0684","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0684.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0684.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrpx-qq9r-w54g/GHSA-mrpx-qq9r-w54g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0684.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88042/info.html","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHNE_17190.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0243.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1020","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1020.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1244","title":"IPFilter 本地任意文件修改漏洞","description":"IPFilter 3.2.3至3.2.10版本中存在文件权限缺陷漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在IPFilter保存输出文件时发起符号链接攻击，利用程序对临时文件处理不当的缺陷，以IPFilter进程权限修改系统任意文件，导致权限提升或系统文件被篡改。该漏洞要求攻击者具有本地系统访问权限，CVSS评分7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1244"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.540","remediation":"立即升级至 IPFilter 3.2.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复保存输出文件时未正确处理符号链接的问题。如无法升级，应确保 IPFilter 运行在专用低权限账户下，避免以 root 运行；同时配置输出目录仅允许 IPFilter 进程本身写入，并定期检查输出文件路径是否被恶意符号链接劫持。此外，使用 nosuid、noexec 挂载选项的临时文件系统存放 IPFilter 输出文件也可作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13303","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1244.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1244","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1244.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1244.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4rc3-c847-cjgp/GHSA-4rc3-c847-cjgp.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87832/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1244.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000609.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87d96785-0cbc-433d-a944-0025d58a8f33.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1020.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1085","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1085.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1369","title":"RealNetworks RealServer 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Real Media RealServer (rmserver) 6.0.3.353 版本存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，该软件将管理员密码以明文形式存储在全局可读的 rmserver.cfg 配置文件中。本地攻击者可通过读取该配置文件获取明文密码，进而利用获取的凭证提升系统权限。该漏洞影响 RealServer 6.0.3.353 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级至最新版本或限制配置文件访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1369"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.603","remediation":"立即将 rmserver.cfg 文件权限从 644 改为 600（仅所有者可读写），命令：chmod 600 /usr/local/rmserver/rmserver.cfg。升级 RealServer 至 7.0 及以上版本（该版本支持加密存储密码）。如无法升级，改用 PAM 或 LDAP 外部认证，避免在配置文件中存储明文密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92411181619110&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1085.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0121","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0121.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0444","title":"Microsoft Windows ARP Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000 的 ARP 协议处理存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标主机发送特制的恶意 ARP 数据包，触发系统弹窗或日志填充，每收到一个恶意数据包即弹出消息框，或导致日志文件被大量记录占满磁盘空间，从而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 Windows 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0444"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.593","remediation":"受影响系统（Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000）均已停止支持，微软不再发布安全补丁。建议立即升级至 Windows 10/11 等受支持版本；在无法升级的环境中，可在网络边界防火墙或交换机上配置 ARP 报文速率限制和异常检测规则，过滤非信任网段的 ARP 广播包，并部署 IDS/IPS 检测恶意 ARP 流量以缓解拒绝服务攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92394891221029&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0121.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0123","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0123.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0446","title":"NetBSD NetBSD VFS 符号链接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.3 及之前版本的 VFS（虚拟文件系统）存在符号链接处理缺陷，本地攻击者可通过 ln 命令创建异常符号链接触发该漏洞，导致系统拒绝服务。由于 VFS 在处理畸形符号链接时未能正确验证其结构，恶意用户可构造特殊链接使内核进入异常状态，造成系统崩溃或服务不可用。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.3.3 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用需本地用户权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0446"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.840","remediation":"升级至 NetBSD 1.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复 VFS 中对异常符号链接处理的缺陷。如无法立即升级，可限制非信任用户的本地登录权限，或通过内核安全模块禁止特殊符号链接创建作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7051"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0123.toml"}]